nginx_memcached_hash 0.01
=========================

Description.


INSTALLATION

  ./configure --add-module=/path/to/nginx_memcached_hash-0.01/


USAGE

    upstream memcached_cluster {
        memcached_hash  ketama_points=150  weight_scale=10;

        server   backend1.example.com:11211   weight=25;
        server   127.0.0.1:11211              max_fails=3  fail_timeout=30s;

        server   unix:/tmp/backend3           down;
    }

And the you use memcached_cluster in memcached_pass directve:

    server {
        location / {
            set             $memcached_key   "$uri?$args";
            memcached_pass  memcached_cluster;
            error_page      404 502 504 = @fallback;
        }

        location = @fallback {
            proxy_pass      http://backend;
        }
    }


SUPPORT
